Community News Aggregator is a WordPress plugin that gives a community/group blog, the power to let its members synchronize their own individual blogs with the community's main blog. The members can write blog posts at their personal blogs, mark it under appropriate synchronize category, and the blog post will appear on the community's blog after being moderated by the blog admin.

Developer: Ashish Dubey(ashish.dubey91@gmail.com)

If you have suggestions or a query, feel free to drop me an email.

